         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot Garden ¶ 30/6/70 ¶  ¶ I ought to have written to you, dear Dr Story, long before this, to acknowledge the safe arrival of the sedges, grasses, waterplants &amp;c which you so kindly secured ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.06.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To George Story</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">DX19, Cotton/Story Papers, University of Tasmania Archives, Hobart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">MS annotation by Story:</seg> Dr Mueller 30/6/79| <name key="Didymotheca%20thesioides">Didymotheca thesioides</name> J. Hkr.</p>
               </note>Melbourne bot Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30/6/70</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I ought to have written to you, dear Dr Story, long before this, to acknowledge the safe arrival of the sedges, grasses, waterplants &amp;c which you so kindly secured this year. I was so much harrassed in my department, that I could really not gain the time for any exclusively botanical matters, this being the planting season and my time much occupied, especially since the Department became so much disorganized.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your collection contains the rare <name key="Didymotheca%20thesioides">Didymotheca thesioides</name>, J Hooker, besides new localities for Ricinocarpus<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Ricinocarpos? <seg style="font-style: italic; ">In Story's hand</seg> (3182) <seg style="font-style: italic; ">above </seg>Ricinocarpus.</p>
               </note> pinifolius [Desfont.], <name key="Caustis%20pentandra">Caustis pentandra</name> RBr, Hierochloa<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Hierochloe? <seg style="font-style: italic; ">In Story's hand</seg> 755 Gram. dysarrhenum Lab 83-t332) <seg style="font-style: italic; ">above </seg>Hierochloa. The reference is to a discussion of a grass [Gramineae abbreviated?], <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Disarrenum antarcticum</seg>, in Labillardère (1804-06), vol 2, p. 83 and plate 232.</p>
               </note> rariflora J Hook., and a few other. So I hope you will feel sufficiently encouraged to watch the plants around you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me hope your health is firm &amp; your mind cheerful.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With best regards</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I hope you got the Cork Oaks &amp;c &amp;c safely through Mr Abbotts mediation</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Caustis%20pentandra">Caustis pentandra</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Didymotheca%20thesioides">Didymotheca thesioides</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Hierochloa%20rariflora">Hierochloa rariflora</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Ricinocarpus%20pinifolius">Ricinocarpus pinifolius</name>
            </p>
